There are many systems along the rim of the galaxy that are little known to us.  The Rebels are likely to use these systems as hiding places from which to spread chaos throughout the galaxy. We can explore these systems by deploying Imperial Probe Droids on Reconnaissance missions there.  We can also employ our capital ships for exploration; these ships risk destruction, however, should they encounter a Rebel fleet.  If our units locate an unpopulated system, a regiment of troopers may be sent via ship to establish a base there.  Building facilities on that system will bring colonists who will be most loyal to the Empire.